{
  "stem": "23942.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I grew up with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Part of the time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whenever I felt like it, I would go there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I knew-- I loved my grandmother more than-- next to my mother, there was nobody I loved more than my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was so close to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so one day, the man took me, and we went on the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a goy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told you, Jews were not allowed to go on a train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember what he said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- I'm sure it was very quiet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was very little conversation, because there wasn't supposed to be.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that, you know-- it was supposed to be like a hush-hush thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the whole thing was that she shouldn't be discovered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, that he's taking a Jewish child out of where he wasn't supposed to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- so he took me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I guess-- I don't remember too much of the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember I went on a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The train from Przemysl to Grodzisko, which was actually [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The station, we came to [NON-ENGLISH], which is the station of Grodzisko.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's where we got off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there, he must have lived in that area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I don't know if I slept maybe one night-- probably, that one night, I slept in his house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't remember much from it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was-- it's-- it's blacked out in my mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I do remember in the morning, when we started to walk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You see, in order to walk from his house to bring me to my grandmother, usually people go on the main road, but we didn't.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember we walked over fields to make a shortcut.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He knew how to hit straight-- a shortcut, the shortest way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we shouldn't be discovered.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
